# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Markdit — environment configuration
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is git-ignored) and fill in the values.
# Only variables prefixed with VITE_ are exposed to the frontend by Vite.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# No environment variables are currently required. Markdit runs fully on-device:
# editing, rendering, slide generation and copy-to-clipboard need no external
# configuration or sign-in.
